Welche Farbe erhält die Überschrift?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>HTML + CSS</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">h2 { color: blue; }
.title { color: green; }
#headline { color: red; }

&lt;h2 id=&quot;headline&quot; class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Start&lt;/h2&gt;</pre></div>

Was bewirkt der Code?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.toolbar {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}</pre></div>

Welche Aussage passt zu diesem Layout?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.cards {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
  gap: 1rem;
}</pre></div>

Welche Darstellung gilt bei 600px Viewportbreite?<br><div class="code-card" style="max-width:900px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;background:#102d42;box-shadow:0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.16);font-family:Consolas,'Courier New',monospace;margin:12px 0;"><div style="height:42px;background:#12334a;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;color:#fff;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-weight:700;"><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ff5f57;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#ffbd2e;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:7px;"></span><span style="width:11px;height:11px;background:#28c840;border-radius:50%;display:inline-block;margin-right:13px;"></span>style.css</div><pre style="margin:0;padding:18px 20px;color:#f8fbff;line-height:1.48;font-size:15px;white-space:pre-wrap;background:#102d42;">.layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
@media (min-width: 800px) {
  .layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
}</pre></div>
